      <title>尽管竞争对手因需求疲软而苦苦挣扎，宝马电动汽车销量仍大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马公司其核心品牌的纯电动汽车第一季度销量大幅增长，为欧洲步履蹒跚的电动汽车市场发出了积极信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bmw-ev-sales-surge-even-as-rivals-struggle-with-weak-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 07:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
